io.doov.core.dsl.field.types

Interface NumericFieldInfo<N extends java.lang.Number>

  • Type Parameters:
    N - the type of the field value
    All Superinterfaces:
    BaseFieldInfo<N>, DslField<N>, Readable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DoubleFieldInfo, FloatFieldInfo, IntegerFieldInfo, LongFieldInfo

    public interface NumericFieldInfo<N extends java.lang.Number>
extends BaseFieldInfo<N>
    Base interface for numeric field info.

    It contains default methods for common checks, which are calls to methods on NumericCondition.
